  <description><![CDATA[<p>The classy Aktivhotel Schweizerhof sits in an elevated position overlooking <a data-udi="umb://document/0424394c50b54ef4848722ee185d0739" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/austria/austrian-tyrol/kitzbuhel" title="Kitzbuhel">Kitzbühel</a>, directly opposite the Hahnenkamm gondola and a short stroll away from the quaint town centre. The hotel has an excellent reputation for cuisine as well as a modern spa area.</p>
<h2>Wellness &amp; dining</h2>
<p>The modern wellness area features three different saunas, a spacious relaxation room, indoor pool with integrated whirlpool, spa treatment room and fitness room. The hotel has a slick and stylish design throughout including in the restaurant, comfortable lobby and the inviting bar. Be sure to explore the extensive wine list.</p>
<p>Spacious bedrooms are comfortable with pine décor and modern design throughout.</p>
<h2><span>Mountain views</span></h2>
<p><span>The Aktivhotel Schweizerhof is in a great position enjoying lovely views of <a data-udi="umb://document/daebb810f1b948b9acb0b1555405cdac" href="/{localLink:umb://document/daebb810f1b948b9acb0b1555405cdac}" title="Kitzbuhel">Kitzbühel</a> and the mountains. Your surroundings can be enjoyed from the stylish front of house sun terrace and restaurant with floor-to-ceiling windows.</span></p>
<p><span>The hotel is located opposite the Hahnenkamm gondola to get the lift up in the morning, and you can ski back to the door in the afternoon. </span><span>The resort </span><span>centre is just a few minutes' downhill walk.</span></p>
<p><span>Photos: © Defrancesco Photography</span></p>]]></description>
