  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard </strong>Austrian twin rooms are around 18<span>m² and have a bath or shower</span></p>
<p><strong>Classic</strong> Austrian twin rooms are around 18-21<span>m² and also have a lounge area with a single sofa bed that can sleep a third person. Rooms have a balcony. </span></p>
<p><span><strong>Comfort</strong> Austrian twin rooms are more spacious at around 25m² and have a balcony. </span></p>
<p><span>Austrian twin beds are one large bed frame containing two single mattresses, both with separate duvets and linen sets, that cannot be separated. In some rooms it may be possible to separate them but this will need to be requested in advance. </span></p>
<p><strong>Bedroom Facilities</strong></p>
